      "span_text": "HIF-1 binds to hypoxia-response elements (HRE) found in promoter or enhancer DNA regions of target hypoxia-inducible genes that include vascular endothelial growth factor (VEGF), glucose transporter-1 (Glut-1), nitric oxide synthases, and likely between 100 and 200 others"
